  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Jujutsu%20Sorcerer.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Even if your target is miles away if you have any remnants of their body they are as good as dead.</p><p> Starting at 7th level, you make a straw doll that you keep on your person used to execute your techniques.</p><p> This straw doll is indestructible and always on your person.</p><p> If a target is bleeding or cursed, you can institute your Straw Doll Technique.</p><p> Using this technique requires a doll and a piece of their body such as blood or hair.</p><p> Once per turn when you would make an attack with your nail, you can make an attack on your straw doll against your opponent's AC at advantage.</p><p> On a success, your hit on the doll resonates within their body and they take damage as if their body had been hit by the attack.</p><p></p>",
